between by a binary factor, which is whole genome doubling here, it's being

242
00:13:58.174 --> 00:13:59.034
removed. And

243
00:14:00.374 --> 00:14:01.904
here we define at least 20

244
00:14:05.074 --> 00:14:07.814
patients with at least two years of follow-up.

245
00:14:08.154 --> 00:14:12.104
So if it doesn't meet that criteria, that cancer type will be removed in the

