00:27:08.458 --> 00:27:11.018
BRCA1 promoter methylation can also help supplement

468
00:27:12.238 --> 00:27:15.418
patient selection there. But for the time being, we see it as

469
00:27:17.078 --> 00:27:20.478
GIS or HR gene mutation kind of

470
00:27:20.778 --> 00:27:22.438
selection logic.

471
00:27:28.558 --> 00:27:32.478
I have another question. So can you comment on, are

472
00:27:32.518 --> 00:27:34.858
there any other assays that have been

