00:28:12.318 --> 00:28:16.158
predictive benefit in a clinical trial or with on-target therapies,

486
00:28:16.218 --> 00:28:20.198
that's to be determined. But there are definitely other

487
00:28:20.278 --> 00:28:20.958
assays that have

488
00:28:22.598 --> 00:28:24.538
shown that already. So we're hoping to show that soon.

489
00:28:25.438 --> 00:28:26.018
